data.description: Need space for living, office, children's play, and an area to watch your favorite movie?  This home meets those requirements!  It has a theatre room and large game room as well as a great room with living, dining, and kitchen combined.  Need primary bedroom privacy?  It is located on the first floor.  All other bedrooms are on the 2nd floor.  Need access to I-45?  You are only minutes away.  There are plenty of community amenities--community center, pool, & playground.  Primary and secondary schools are a walking distance away. Come check out this great home today!
